overview: As the title suggests, Rocco's keepin' it real with a little help from his friends, in this case African-American stud Mike Chapman and his counterpart Euro-Black cocksman Franco Roccaforte, AKA "Teo". The two brothas from anotha motha' meet Rocco in Prague where he's decided to take his vacation to get away from all the stress... the three journeyman take in the local sights, including gorgeous Czech mate Defrancesca, natural breasted brunettes Angelica Black, Jassy and Kattie Gold, butch schoolgirl Nikita and blue eyed beauty Rachel. For lovers of hairy bush, and we mean very hairy bush, there's Nataly who treats Teo to a game of hide and seek. Like some renegade from the 70's, ...
title: Rocco's Reality in Prague
